622
00:57:44.665 --> 00:57:45.666
Papa!

623
00:57:46.233 --> 00:57:47.299
I'm here!

624
00:57:47.301 --> 00:57:48.970
Listen to my voice, Papa!

625
00:58:03.217 --> 00:58:04.518
Papa!

626
00:58:05.720 --> 00:58:07.188
