742
01:08:27.508 --> 01:08:28.574
<i>Clear.</i>

743
01:08:35.215 --> 01:08:37.518
Three, two, one.
Execute.

744
01:09:03.310 --> 01:09:04.512
Target neutralized.

745
01:09:05.680 --> 01:09:06.781
