I'm doing this.

764
01:11:10.738 --> 01:11:12.505
Get the strike squad.

765
01:11:12.507 --> 01:11:13.608
Check the control room.

766
01:11:29.123 --> 01:11:30.323
Last one up.

767
01:11:31.025 --> 01:11:32.325
Hope they all work.

768
01:11:42.870 --> 01:11:44.036
RV's clear.

769
01:11:44.038 --> 01:11:46.739
Ethan, strike squad
