773
01:12:03.423 --> 01:12:04.924
Ethan, do you hear me?

774
01:12:04.926 --> 01:12:06.491
Get out, now!

775
01:12:06.493 --> 01:12:07.494
Move!

776
01:12:26.981 --> 01:12:28.581
