any second.

778
01:12:29.951 --> 01:12:31.018
Kid, if you hear me...

779
01:12:32.452 --> 01:12:33.486
we have to go.

780
01:12:34.755 --> 01:12:35.823
I'm sorry.

781
01:12:37.124 --> 01:12:38.524
