785
01:12:48.669 --> 01:12:49.802
<i>Security breach.</i>

786
01:12:49.804 --> 01:12:51.639
They're here
for the VIPs.

787
01:12:52.607 --> 01:12:54.041
Go to the construction site.

788
01:12:54.709 --> 01:12:55.710
